# ── Build artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
**/target/
dist/
*.dmg
*.exe
*.zip

# ── Secrets / runtime state — NEVER publish ───────────────────────────────
# Wallet keystores carry seed material; node runtime dirs carry chain data.
**/keystore.json
**/testnet.json
**/sim-actors.json
**/node.pid
**/blocks.log
**/data/
# Generated dev/test net working dirs (regenerable via `sov-testnet`).
chain/testnet/node-*/
chain/simnet/node-*/
explorer/devnet/node-*/
# Anything that looks like a private key or environment secret.
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
.env
.env.*
*.seed

# ── OS / editor noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# Nested project with its own git history (separate agent) — not part of this repo
dashboard/dash2/
